title: Provided however, that restrictions on height spelt out in this Regulations shall not be applicable
clause_text: Provided however, that restrictions on height spelt out in this Regulations shall not be applicable for reconstruction and redevelopment undertaken underRegulations33(5), 33(6), 33(7), 33(7)(A),,33(9),33(9)(B),33(10),33(10) (A),33(11),33(15)and33(20) (A)of
